Okay so i never update but its okay cause im sure no one really cares. but anyway i have a story for whoever reads about my cousin, amy.

It alllll started about 9 years ago...

I was at my grandmas for Thanksgiving din din. When my uncle alan arrives with a girl i had never seen before. He introduced her to everyone and i found at that she was his daughter. Me being only 6 i didnt understand why she has never been around before, but then again i didnt really care. She was amazing. She was athletic, pretty, and had the best personality of anyone i had ever met. I fell in love with her. She didnt live in beckley so i rarely got to spend much time with her. When we met she 18 and a senior in high school. After she graduated she went to college and i seen her even less then, but we stayed in touch. Sometimes she would spend the weekend with our family and her and i would go outside and play basketball, and just have fun (or atleast i did, i was probably annoying to her at the time). 
One summer she came in for the entire summer. which was probably the greatest thing that had ever happened to me. I had a blast that summer, but ofcourse it was only the summer and in the middle of august she had to go back up and start school again. Slowly we started to talk less and less, but not because of me, i tried to contact her every chance i got. but after a while she completely quit calling me, quit emailing me, and quit coming to see me. I was only like 9 so i was devastated because she was my best friend. 
About 3 yrs after the last time i had talked to her, she just shows up out of nowhere because one of her dads friends has passed. Anyway as upset as i had been with her for not staying in touch with me, i was so excited because i knew we would keep in touch this time. She stayed for about 3 days and then left. And the same thing happened again. 
Another 2 yrs went by and i hadnt talked to her at all. I didnt even try. I missed her, but i had grown up quite a bit and it didnt bother me near as much. I kind of understood.  
About a  month ago i was bored and started thinking about her and decided to type her email into the search bar on myspace. Sure enough there she was. Only one problem. she hadnt logged in since may, but i thought what the heck? it couldnt hurt to try. so i sent her a msg and about 2 wks later she msgs me back. apologizing for everything, and whatnot. its pretty nice talking to her, and cathcing up and all. Its just kinda hard getting over how bad she hurt me then. But im trying to forgive and forget and hope it doesnt happen again.

anyway, thats my story
